12:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='718627' id='t-718627'>And he said, &quot;What?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720841' id='t-720841'>And I said, &quot;A psychopath.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722169' id='t-722169'>And I said, &quot;I've got a list
