<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726572' id='t-726572'>Can I go through them with you?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729393' id='t-729393'>And he looked intrigued despite himself,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731510' id='t-731510'>and he said, &quot;Okay, go on.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732909' id='t-732909'>And I said, &quot;Okay.
