</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742524' id='t-742524'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='746699' id='t-746699'>He said, &quot;Well, you've
got to believe in you!&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749756' id='t-749756'>And I said, &quot;Manipulative.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='752668' id='t-752668'>He said, &quot;That's leadership.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='754385' id='t-754385'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='755410' id='t-755410'>And I said, &quot;Shallow affect,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757840' id='t-757840'>an inability to experience
a range of emotions.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='760136' id='t-760136'>He said, &quot;Who wants to be weighed
down by some nonsense emotions?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763766' id='t-763766'>So he was going down
