</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='769186' id='t-769186'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772302' id='t-772302'>But I did notice something happening
to me the day I was with Al Dunlap.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='775746' id='t-775746'>Whenever he said anything to me
