<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='778667' id='t-778667'>like he said &quot;no&quot; to juvenile delinquency,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781634' id='t-781634'>he said he got accepted into West Point,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783564' id='t-783564'>and they don't let
delinquents in West Point.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='786443' id='t-786443'>He said &quot;no&quot; to many short-term
marital relationships.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789183' id='t-789183'>He's only ever been married twice.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790867' id='t-790867'>Admittedly, his first wife
