<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='883607' id='t-883607'>And he said, &quot;I'm not a psychopath.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885585' id='t-885585'>He said, &quot;You know what?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='886768' id='t-886768'>One of the items on the checklist
