<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='904321' id='t-904321'>He said, &quot;I've got a tribunal coming up.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='906580' id='t-906580'>Will you come to it?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='908740' id='t-908740'>So I said okay.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:21
</data>
